title: Harry og kammertjeneren - Harry and the Butler (1961 - Denmark)
description:
Harry og kammertjeneren (1961 - Denmark)                   Harry and the Butler

Comedy / Family
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0054965/


Academy Awards Oscar - NOMINATED - Best Foreign Language Film

Harry is a simple old-time shop porter offered a chance at self-realisation when he's bequeathed a sum by an unknown relative (via several levels of fiscal blood suckers). He decides to engage a butler to take good care of him for a time. This is a man of distinguished upper class service, but a generous nature which happily integrates with Harry's small but colourful world of drinking buddies and crackpot neighbourhood kids.
